  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't earn my living, because we lived from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the savings, you know, what we got.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got a few gold pieces, jewelry, little by little, start selling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got the apartment, which Persian carpets, all kind of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's where we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, always customer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the war, are you kidding?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got the junk, you can sell, black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Don't forget, in Poland, you always try to have some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dollars, you know, and insurance or something, in case, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How could you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tell you, we were good off, I mean well-off, nice living, nice family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father was well-- a nice guy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a lot of friends, never came to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, listen, they were all the time some kind searching in houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came and they started beating up people, killing people once in awhile, with the help of the Polacks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They helped them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't pleasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I left Krakow when we had to leave Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this governor Frank decided he wants to have a capital Krakow city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave an order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He can keep only 10,000 people, like tailors, shoemakers, painters, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what made us to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we couldn't prove are we tailors or something like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we left the town near Tarnow, which was a small town, a little town where my mother spent her youth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
